Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}-3天過去了-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼還在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小百合真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你能擔任首領
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連你們都在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影子不是已經消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不會有妨礙你們的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是還在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但百合的心結可能已經解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎 百合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 呃 那個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓我用催眠術讓你坦白…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看她不情願的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是首領
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼容易就解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豈不是惹人笑話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就用催眠術…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 承認了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏你好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是百合喜歡鬧彆扭罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還蠻開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你叫我百合了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 就像朋友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 我們的準備沒有白費咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後有件想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏說她還沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnmingliu\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs100\pos(640,680)}畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有大家幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也費了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那是神技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嘴上不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但大家還蠻享受這邊的生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我明白了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也多虧了小百合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高松也走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然變成了NPC 但恢復意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不怎麼吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說變成NPC就沒法恢復了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來設定成了憑藉強大意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天能變回人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才工作時也在唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩澤最後唱的那首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全校廣播的那首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是首好歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體育館？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\1c&H000000&\bord0\pos(640,591)}死後世界戰線 畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字是奏負責
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 你沒畢過業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想會很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點意思都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你寫字時還蠻開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女生大都會哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 所以說女人這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為換衣服是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想真會消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒做好思想準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 這也算是原首領嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大家消失後 你就沒有領袖的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實有什麼變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像個女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該高興嗎 還是應該發火？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥結束後 變回連這個都不知道的天真女孩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小百合也有可愛的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百合真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致開幕詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在舉行在死後世界戰鬥至今的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死後世界戰線畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 齊唱戰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰歌？ 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死後世界戰線的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是代替校歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有讓人寫過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是奏寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說你根本不是戰線成員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 傳一下歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,校歌都差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便唱一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從天上的死後戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由閒人成員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為您廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死前一定要試吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪門子歌詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰來事先檢查一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會唱出來耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏也是費了好一番工夫寫出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得這麼過分嘛 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫的認真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這上面不是寫著「閒人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺字裡行間包含著奏的感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到尾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頒發畢業證書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也基本是奏做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 頒發證書的校長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 是我猜拳輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼總是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因為由你做最合適
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頒發畢業證書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 立華奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲村百合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這副打扮很合適你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\bord0\frz3\move(1012,387,1035,337)}畢\N業\N證\N書
